text: int main ( ) { long int a [ 100000 ] , c , b , i , j , k , l , n , e , f , m ; scanf ( "%d" , & n ) ; for ( i = 1 ; i <= n ; i ++ ) { scanf ( "%d" , & a [ i ] ) ; } e = n ; c = 0 ; l = 0 ; for ( i = 1 ; i <= n ; i ++ ) { f = 1 ; e = n - c ; while ( f < e ) { m = 1 ; b = 0 ; k = 0 ; for ( j = i + 1 ; m <= f ; j ++ ) { if ( a [ i + b ] <= a [ j ] ) { k ++ ; } m ++ ; b ++ ; } f ++ ; if ( k == f - 1 ) l ++ ; } e -- ; c ++ ; } printf ( "%d" , l + n ) ; return 0 ; }
